com.opera.core.systems.model

Class ScreenCaptureReply.Builder

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.opera.core.systems.model.ScreenCaptureReply.Builder
  • Enclosing class:
    ScreenCaptureReply

    public static class ScreenCaptureReply.Builder
extends Object
    A builder for creating screen capture reply instances. Example: 
    
   ScreenCaptureReply.Builder builder = ScreenCaptureReply.builder();
   builder.setBlank(true);
   builder.setCrashed(true);
   ScreenCaptureReply reply = builder.build();
